<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Free Homebuying Masterclass | Jahar Asad</title>
<meta name="description" content="Free live first-time homebuyer masterclass with Jahar Asad, The Realtor & Mortgage Man, July 28, 2026 at 7:00 PM Eastern.">
<style>
:root{--navy:#0A1628;--gold:#C9A84C;--cream:#F7F3EA;--ink:#172033}
*{box-sizing:border-box} body{margin:0;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.55}
.wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:auto;padding:0 22px} header{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;border-bottom:4px solid var(--gold)}
.nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:18px 0} .brand{font-weight:800} .brand small{display:block;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:.08em}
.hero{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy),#173a66);color:white} .hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.15fr .85fr;align-items:center;min-height:630px}
h1,h2{font-family:Georgia,serif} h1{font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.6rem);line-height:1.03;margin:12px 0} h1 span{color:var(--gold)}
.lead{font-size:1.17rem;max-width:680px;color:#e8eef8} .details{display:flex;gap:18px;flex-wrap:wrap;font-weight:700;margin:24px 0}
.btn{display:inline-block;background:var(--gold);color:var(--navy);padding:14px 24px;border-radius:999px;font-weight:900;text-decoration:none;border:0;cursor:pointer}
.photo{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:flex-end;height:630px} .photo img{max-height:610px;object-fit:contain}
.strip{background:var(--gold);padding:10px} .strip img{width:100%;max-height:120px;object-fit:contain}
section{padding:70px 0} .alt{background:var(--cream)} .head{text-align:center;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto 34px} .head h2{font-size:2.5rem;color:var(--navy);margin:0 0 10px}
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:18px} .card{background:#fff;border:1px solid #e7dfcd;border-radius:18px;padding:22px;box-shadow:0 10px 28px rgba(10,22,40,.07)}
.card h3{color:var(--navy);margin-top:0} .register{display:grid;grid-template-columns:.8fr 1.2fr;gap:30px} .side{background:var(--navy);color:white;padding:28px;border-radius:20px}
.qr{background:white;padding:12px;border-radius:16px;max-width:220px;margin:20px auto} form{border:1px solid #e7dfcd;border-radius:20px;padding:28px;box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(10,22,40,.12)}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px} .full{grid-column:1/-1} label{display:block;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:6px} input,select,textarea{width:100%;padding:12px;border:1px solid #cfd5df;border-radius:9px;font:inherit} textarea{min-height:100px}
footer{background:#06101f;color:#cbd5e1;padding:34px 0;text-align:center} @media(max-width:850px){.hero-grid,.register{grid-template-columns:1fr}.photo{height:460px}.photo img{max-height:440px}.cards{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}
@media(max-width:560px){.cards,.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.full{grid-column:auto}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header><div class="wrap nav"><div class="brand">Jahar Asad<small>The Realtor &amp; Mortgage Man™</small></div><a class="btn" href="#register">Free Masterclass</a></div></header>
<main>
<section class="hero"><div class="wrap hero-grid">
<div><div style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase">Free Live Homebuying Masterclass</div>
<h1>Buying Your First Home <span>Doesn't Have to Be Complicated.</span></h1>
<p class="lead">Learn the process, understand common financing options, and leave with a practical roadmap—without pressure or confusing jargon.</p>
<div class="details"><span>📅 Tuesday, July 28, 2026</span><span>🕖 7:00 PM Eastern</span><span>💻 Live Online</span></div>
<a class="btn" href="#register">Save My Free Seat</a></div>
<div class="photo"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Jahar Asad"></div>
</div></section>
<div class="strip"><div class="wrap"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Professional credentials and brand logos"></div></div>

<section class="alt"><div class="wrap"><div class="head"><h2>What You'll Learn</h2><p>A clear, practical introduction to the decisions first-time buyers face.</p></div>
<div class="cards">
<div class="card"><h3>Preparing to Buy</h3><p>Budget, credit, savings, and the documents you may need.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Mortgage Options</h3><p>FHA, Conventional, VA, USDA, and down payment assistance basics.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Finding Your Home</h3><p>Home search strategy, offers, inspections, and appraisal.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Closing Confidently</h3><p>Closing costs, final walkthrough, and what happens on closing day.</p></div>
</div></div></section>

<section><div class="wrap"><div class="head"><h2>Meet Jahar Asad</h2><p><strong>The Realtor &amp; Mortgage Man™</strong></p></div>
<p style="max-width:780px;margin:auto;text-align:center">As both a licensed Realtor® and Mortgage Loan Officer, I help buyers understand how the home search and financing process work together. My goal is to educate first, answer your questions, and help you make informed decisions when you are ready to purchase.</p>
</div></section>

<section class="alt" id="register"><div class="wrap register">
<div class="side"><h2 style="font-size:2.2rem;margin-top:0">Save My Free Seat</h2><p>Complete the form to reserve your place. Your confirmation and event details will be sent by email.</p>
<div class="qr"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Registration QR code"></div></div>
<form name="homebuying-masterclass-registration" method="POST" action="/masterclass-thank-you.html" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
<input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="homebuying-masterclass-registration"><p hidden><label>Do not fill this out: <input name="bot-field"></label></p>
<div class="grid">
<div><label>First Name</label><input name="first-name" required></div>
<div><label>Last Name</label><input name="last-name" required></div>
<div><label>Email</label><input type="email" name="email" required></div>
<div><label>Mobile Phone</label><input type="tel" name="phone" required></div>
<div class="full"><label>When are you hoping to buy?</label><select name="timeline" required><option value="">Select one</option><option>Within 90 days</option><option>3–6 months</option><option>6–12 months</option><option>More than 12 months</option><option>Just learning</option></select></div>
<div class="full"><label>What concerns you most?</label><select name="concern" required><option value="">Select one</option><option>Down payment</option><option>Credit</option><option>Monthly payment</option><option>Finding the right home</option><option>Understanding the process</option></select></div>
<div class="full"><label>Your biggest question (optional)</label><textarea name="question"></textarea></div>
</div>
<p><label style="font-weight:400"><input type="checkbox" name="updates" value="yes" style="width:auto"> Send me educational emails and masterclass updates.</label></p>
<button class="btn" type="submit">Save My Free Seat</button>
</form></div></section>
</main>
<footer><div class="wrap"><strong>Jahar Asad | The Realtor &amp; Mortgage Man™</strong><br>919-200-3359<br><small>Realtor® | Mortgage Loan Officer NMLS #2112298 | Equal Housing Lender. Educational event; program eligibility and terms vary.</small></div></footer>
</body></html>
